    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1961-04-18T16:52:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1961-04-18T16:52:00-05:00" n="126"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d126">
                <head>126. Telegram From the Commander in Chief, Atlantic (<persName
                        corresp="#p_DARL1" type="from">Dennison</persName>) to the Commander, Key
                    West Forces (<persName type="to">McElroy</persName>)<note n="0" type="source"
                        xml:id="d126fn0">Source: Naval Historical Center, Area Files, Bumpy Road
                        Materials. Top Secret; Operational Immediate. Repeated to <gloss
                            target="#t_JCS1">JCS</gloss>, COMNAVB <gloss target="#t_GTMO1"
                            >GTMO</gloss>, and <gloss target="#t_CTG1">CTG</gloss> 81.8.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Norfolk</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1961-04-18T16:52:00-05:00">April 18, 1961, 4:52 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>182152Z. Bumpy Road. Exclusive for <persName>RAdm McElroy</persName>
                    <gloss target="#t_info1">info</gloss>
                    <persName>RAdms OʼDonnell</persName>, <persName corresp="#p_CRAJE1"
                        >Clark</persName>, Gen <persName corresp="#p_GMGDW1">Gray</persName> from
                        <persName corresp="#p_DARL1">Dennison</persName>. Up to 4 <gloss
                        target="#t_MIG1">MIG</gloss>s have been reported in the objective area. In
                    the event we have to give support against <gloss target="#t_MIG1">MIG</gloss>s
                    desire you paint out US markings on six F3 H, arm them with Sidewinders and/or
                    Sparrows and prepare them for combat operations in the objective area by
                    daylight 19 April. Any launch directive will be issued by <gloss
                        target="#t_CINCLANTFLT1">CINCLANTFLT</gloss>. Hold close and try conceal
                    above preparatory measures.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
